== 評價 ==
《叛將風雲》在評論界的評價褒貶不一，該片在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]的新鮮度52%，基於117條專業影評，平均分為5.6/10，多數好評傾向觀眾，觀眾評比分數74%，平均分3.8/5<ref name="tomatoes">{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/last_castle|title=Last Castle|work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2022-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917075736/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/last_castle|dead-url=no|archive-date=2020-09-17}}</ref>，在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]則根據32條評論獲得43分（滿分100分），代表「褒貶不一或中庸」<ref name="metacritic">{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-last-castle |title=Last Castle |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2022-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211224161007/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-last-castle |archive-date=2021-12-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

